Class ClientProperty

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ethercis.servicemanager.common.EncodableData
      • com.ethercis.servicemanager.common.ClientProperty
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public final class ClientProperty
extends EncodableData
    This class encapsulates one client property, for example query parameters The parameters are passed logonservice key value pair with an optional encoding id and a type If the attribute type is missing we assume a 'String' property
